Review: *I* would die for young, punk Joaquin
I actually didn’t watch this today but I did have a couple-months-long period in my teens where I watched it everyday before bed. Just giving it it’s belated 5-stars.
Sam thinks this is a Christmas movie????

It was good but I wanted it to be better. Make no mistake, I wept the last 20 minutes and the whole walk home. But still . . . maybe it was the script? Love to see Zac Efron winning. Devastating at every turn but Stanley Simon’s Mike von Erich really broke my heart 💔
movies are so fun. will be thinking about this costuming for a looooong time.
Can we please bring back glamour
rizz god Gene Kelly does it again. Why did we let actors stop dancing?
We’ll have to muddle through somehow, I guess
Forgot to report that I’ve watched this a month ago but I haven’t stopped thinking about it since!
